	abstract = {Summary The emphasis on corporate cost containment and productivity enhancement during the past decade has prompted AP professionals to seek new ways to automate traditionally paper-based, labor-intensive processes. This chapter explores several of the AP automation solutions. First, it reviews the functionality to consider when automating the readers' AP and procure to pay (P2P) process. There are several types of automation solutions for the P2P process. The chapter looks at the solutions available today and highlights the benefits. It describes other types of AP Automation to consider. Many organizations utilize several types of automation to streamline their end-to-end AP process. All imaging and workflow automation (IWA) solutions share the goal of improving organizations' management of their invoice receipt-to-pay processes. However, not every solution follows the same approach or provides similar functionality at each step of the process. Therefore, accounts payable professionals should understand the major forms that IWA can take.},
